Step 2: Document Mitigation Strategies
Key defensive measures:

Disable Print Spooler: Stop and disable on non-print servers
Apply Patches: Install KB5005010 and later updates
Network Segmentation: Restrict RPC access between systems
Monitor Authentication: Alert on unusual authentication patterns
Disable NTLM: Use Kerberos where possible
