Troubleshooting Tips
Issue: Responder not capturing hashes

Solution: Verify network interface configuration
Solution: Check firewall rules allow SMB traffic
Solution: Ensure target can reach listener IP
Issue: Permission denied errors

Solution: Run Responder with sudo privileges
Solution: Verify file permissions on scripts
Issue: Connection timeouts

Solution: Confirm IP aliases are configured
Solution: Check services are listening on correct ports
Solution: Verify no port conflicts exist
